Text::Rhombus
=============

Draw an alphanumerical rhombus.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install
   
SCRIPTS

bin/rhombus.pl

Interface to Text::Rhombus that contains 
predefined options and outputs a rhombus.

